minijava.typecheck.symboltable
类 MethodTable

java.lang.Object
  minijava.typecheck.symboltable.SymbolTable
      minijava.typecheck.symboltable.MethodTable

public class MethodTable
extends SymbolTable

Identified by method name and class name. Usage: Insert and find parameters and variables of this method.
Used via "(any instance of SymbolTable).globalTable.getClassTable(class name).getMethodTable(this method name)" (Recommended)

作者：
ZongZiWang
